name: Stefan Krajczar
note:
Company name: FoxxBase GmbH

Contact person: Stefan Krajczar

Company website: https://foxxbase.com

Country-Location: Austria

Target audience: mainly Austrian, German, the Russian market

Immediate requirement: "We are looking for a full stack coder, especially PHP, WordPress, WooCommerce, Shopware." 

Future needs: Stefan is interested in lead generation manager with the knowledge of German

During the call we also interviewed 2 candidates:

George https://rh-s.com/web-developer/full-stack-developers/georgy-t/
Has a good experience in PHP, has 3 years of experience in the commercial field, including an e-commerce project built in OpenCart. Knows ReactJs, Rest API, IPR system, CRM system well.

Natan https://rh-s.com/web-developer/back-end-developers/natan-m/
Has 1 year of experience in PHP. Knows C#, Pascal, JS. He can create some bots on Python too.

Stefan liked George the most because he has the wider experience and seems to be a serious specialist.

Start date: on 16th of August, part-time
(Concerning lead gen manager - follow up on 11th of August)
